{
  "texts": [
    "The first agent responsible was categorization, which only ran once and did not participate in the answer-generation process.",
    "Therefore, time and words were not recorded for this agent.",
    "For the second and third agents, as their results mainly involved returning potential content from the guidelines and \"True/ False\" answers, the words was not recorded as well.",
    "The direct question-and-answer design was based on GPT-4, utilizing the same environment as GPT-agents.",
    "Within the design, all questions were posed within a \"for\" loop (similarly to in GPT-agents group), and GPT-4 directly generated responses (Fig. 1B)."
  ]
}